                  <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                  <seg type="rubrication">
                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word for God is not rubricated in the Psalms</desc>
                  <desc>There is columetric layout in the 10th biblical canticle, <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1566hababa#ThreeYouths3"/> and in <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2000Mazmur#Chp150"/></desc>
                  </handNote>
